    public class WindTurbineConnector
extends EnergyProviderConnector
implements IWindTurbine
    The class WindTurbineConnector implements a connector between the IController and the IWindTurbine interfaces.

    Description

    It implements the required interface IController and in the methods it calls the corresponding offered method IWindTurbine.
